      <div class="faq-quote-block-left">
        <div class="faq-quote-image">
          <%= image_tag 'people/alec-ortiz', alt: 'Alec Ortiz', class: 'full-rounded' %>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-quote-inner bg-light-grat">
          <p>"iX was an opportunity to grow and discover – to explore a dynamic and captivating country, develop practical technical skills, and leave behind the comfort of the familiar to join a diverse assembly of scholars, artists, and adventurers at the edge of the world."</p>
          <p><em>– Alec Ortiz, Stanford, iX '15</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-quote-block-left">
        <div class="faq-quote-image">
          <%= image_tag 'people/molly-davey', alt: 'Molly Davey', class: 'full-rounded' %>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-quote-inner">
          <p>"iXperience was hands down the best summer of my life. It's more than just a startup founded by passionate young professionals; it's an experience that every zealous college student should seek out. I intended to come to Cape Town for eight weeks and leave with the knowledge of a new coding language. Instead, I adopted an entirely new lifestyle and outlook on life. I learned a new programming language, worked for a non-profit, went skydiving, jumped off the tallest bungee bridge in the world, dove with great white sharks, attempted surfing, rode an elephant, and came away with so much more."</p>
